{"tid":730292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(達哥徒弟) 有個細路係商場練習足球絕學—牛尾巴","createTime":"2018-07-05T09:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T09:38:49.000Z","uid":11966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f8053837d56e77b2dad4ef56e9b9443c1da2d7","tid":730292,"uid":11966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"只見佢口中念念有詞，並一邊使出牛尾巴步法，<br />\n雖然佢腳中無波，但心中有波，<br />\n隨著時間越慢，佢嘅速度就越快，<br />\n向左，向右，將身體融入呢個節奏。<br />\n不出所料，佢走到我面前企圖越過我堅固嘅防守，<br />\n但我又點會咁容易就比你過去！<br />\n結果我應聲到地。牛尾巴，果然厲害。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/muGDEfwJ1bA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmuGDEfwJ1bA&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwu9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6bb0060c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/muGDEfwJ1bA</a>"},{"pid":"511fcd16dee5b870309581c875b88cf9b4131fb4","tid":730292,"uid":157000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"叫番直角假身型啲"}]}